    <item>
      <title>美国亚马逊 Prime 会员资格在平静期过后增长 8% 创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/amazon-prime-memberships-in-us-gain-8-to-new-high-after-lull</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2014 年以来一直跟踪亚马逊会员情况的消费者情报研究合作伙伴 (Consumer Intelligence Research Partners) 的数据显示，亚马逊公司的 Prime 订阅服务 3 月份美国购物者数量创下新高，达到 1.8 亿，同比增长 8%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/amazon-prime-memberships-in-us-gain-8-to-new-high-after-lull</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟报告支持电信整合和强劲的能源市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/eu-report-calls-for-telecom-consolidation-strong-energy-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据欧盟委托撰写的一份关于竞争力的报告，欧盟应考虑对电信运营商进行整合，以此作为改善欧盟移动和固定网络的一种方式，并应进一步整合其能源市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/eu-report-calls-for-telecom-consolidation-strong-energy-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:24:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>扎克伯格在元成瘾诉讼中避免个人责任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/zuckerberg-avoids-personal-liability-in-meta-addiction-suits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·扎克伯格在大约两打诉讼中赢得了避免个人责任的诉讼，这些诉讼指控 Meta Platforms Inc. 和其他社交媒体公司让儿童对其产品上瘾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/zuckerberg-avoids-personal-liability-in-meta-addiction-suits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 22:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
